Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一到夜晚  四周就变得一片漆黑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天月亮好像也去休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.75,0:02:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.94,0:02:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠又穿越了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.77,0:02:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那么笨手笨脚的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  她又搞砸了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  这里是艾蒿托儿所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事我应该已经拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.85,0:03:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是开园时间  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠又跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又跌倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土鸠  在这严肃的时刻你在搞什么飞机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠  拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠鸠  小鸠鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  满里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.32,0:03:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连环画  能熟练地读出来就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  总有一天会做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能让大家开心  我想练习一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本书我可以借走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力读得更熟练的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只萤火虫孤零零地生活了很久很久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己是一只萤火虫都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人孤零零的很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这一片漆黑的日子里  感觉好像曾经遇到过一件很棒的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问找我有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能别读了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你别读那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个讨厌的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚才的那个大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那是怎么了  和刚才的感觉相差很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有什么烦恼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没有家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上  不久之前我也曾在公园住过一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了清花老师和千岁小姐的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在睡上了软软的被子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.48,0:05:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被子果然很棒呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您不介意的话  要不要来我家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想受来历不明的人的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是花户小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:05:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是猪尾吕义先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没空陪你疯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为什么会生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤火虫在远处发现了一丝美丽的光亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.97,0:06:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一边想「那是什么呢」  一边靠近…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然笨笨的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又睡过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是从头到脚都笨得要死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是迟到了又要被藤本挖苦了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？我们是来讨债的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  债？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎不太妙啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜欢小孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃啊  吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞了人连句对不起都不说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么…放手…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许碰孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤本…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢小瞧我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该已经说过  请你们不要在开园时间过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还敢命令我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.04,0:08:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对的是你们这些不还钱的吧  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太得意忘形了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的社长可是很好心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事请在闭园后再说  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你把该还的钱还清  我们立刻就走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点还钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:08:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.75,0:09:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没空陪小鬼玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啧  这个女人是怎么搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察叔叔  快来救我啊  有可怕的人在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们今天暂且回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要你不还钱  我们还会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您没事吧  清花老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俊彦  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我装哭的  所以没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想只要喊警察叔叔  他们就会回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊  他们真的回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俊彦好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦  要是他们再敢来  就由我来把他们赶走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对土鸠来说  做得还不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我要这样呆到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的电话是那帮家伙打的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清花老师很烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么我能做的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  假如把钱还清  就能治愈清花老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在那种地方坐着  真不知他在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您哪里不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:12:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你操心  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么我能帮您的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您有什么烦恼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么烦恼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是喜欢待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的那本连环画…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从托儿所借来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有在练习但总是读得不太熟练
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过叫你别读了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很喜欢这个故事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想要熟练地读出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你别再读了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这么讨厌这本连环画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么藤本会来这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我住在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是邻居吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看便知吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公园有一位男士说叫我别读这本连环画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到森先生了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猪尾吕义先生怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是指那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是画那本书的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这附近也是颇有名气的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.97,0:13:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是  为什么会叫我不要读这本书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.35,0:13:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  听说那本书是他画的最后一本  之后就再也没画过新书了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的…书？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在美丽的河畔  住着一只萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只萤火虫孤零零地生活了很久很久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己是一只萤火虫都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个不见月亮的漆黑夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只萤火虫在远处发现了一丝美丽的光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一边想「那是什么呢」  一边靠近一看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那是一只虫子的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「真漂亮呢  你是什么虫子？」他这样问道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「和你一样是萤火虫哦」那个女孩子答道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后又问了萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「为什么你不会发光呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直一个人孤零零的萤火虫忘记了如何发光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤火虫的女孩子教会了那只悲伤的萤火虫发光的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那之后两人就在河畔一边发着光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边和和睦睦地一起生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大叔也忘记了如何发光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道理由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这本书里的萤火虫一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能为他做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}友好图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}萤火虫的生态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您今晚有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去看萤火虫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在八幡山的河边等您
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤火虫想起来了「我是萤火虫啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我也可以像你一样发光啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变熟练了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以想起来的  发光的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…被逼无奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  萤火虫还没有出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要说那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一起去看萤火虫吧  在八幡山的河边等您」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.12,0:16:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奈绪子一样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈绪子…小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是…我的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那幅画  那幅画是奈绪子画的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她说萤火虫的故事好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才由我先写出故事  之后她再画出画来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去看萤火虫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  一起去看萤火虫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是约好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这种话  我找到那个地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在八幡山的河边等你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  是  是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果我还是没能去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候我很忙  一直赶着截稿日期
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那您的恋人一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:18:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常漂亮  也想让我看看  她是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈绪子画的画总是让人觉得很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也重新写成了寂寞而又美丽的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后出版成书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:17.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在那之后的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于取得休假了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我还在那个公园等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈绪子  喂  奈绪子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.39,0:18:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飒太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想要的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么我都会拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤火虫…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起去看萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那个时候我没和她一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明明是那样想要和我一起去看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.94,0:19:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一会  再等一会的话一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.93,0:19:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈绪子是站在这里画的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  你没看过萤火虫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.91,0:20:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.91,0:20:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一起去看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是要亲眼看一次才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近已经没有萤火虫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会让你看到  约好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮呢  萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.32,0:21:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔想起发光的方法了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:21:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始写书了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.43,0:22:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为证据  看看这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说那位大叔被治愈了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮上森先生的忙了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.48,0:22:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次毫无疑问100分…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.98,0:22:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.64,0:22:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣去在图书馆对老子的所作所为
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鸠  80分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.69,0:22:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也会对你严格要求的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  小鸠会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.87,0:22:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你对老子做出那种事  给你80分会不会太惯你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.78,0:22:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是给个50分左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.21,0:22:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  80分就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.70,0:22:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,79分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  太微妙了
